svg.text: Little Li is an avid online shopper. Recap what’s in her shopping cart based on the images below,
Xiǎo Lǐ xiǎng mǎi yí jiàn xīn yīfu.
Then share what’s on your online wish list with the class and explain why you want the items, e.g.:
我喜欢白色/我没有白色的裤子，
所以我想买一条白色的裤子。
Wǒ xǐhuān báisè/Wǒ méiyǒu báisè de kùzi, suǒyǐ wǒ xiǎng mǎi yì tiáo báisè de kùzi.
In pairs, identify to whom the objects belong. Use
Zhè píng kělè shì shéi de?
Zhè píng kělè shì Gāo Wénzhōng de.
Then identify the colors of Little Wang’s belongings, using
小王的笔是什么颜色的？
Xiǎo Wáng de bǐ shì shénme yánsè de?
Xiǎo Wáng de bǐ shì huángsè de.
